          <div class="ps5-cost-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 0-6.74 2.74L3 8"/><path d="M3 3v5h5"/><path d="M12 7v5l4 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ps5-cost-title">Lower Your PS5 Repair Cost With a Trade-In</h3>
          <p class="ps5-cost-body">Trade in phones, tablets, consoles, or laptops — even broken ones — to reduce today's repair cost.</p>
          <p class="ps5-cost-note">Get paid via Cash, E-Transfer, or Store Credit</p>
          <a href="/trade-in" class="ps5-trade-in-btn">
            Lower My PS5 Repair Cost
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
