      <div class="ps5-pricing-context">
        <p class="ps5-context-paragraph">PS5 repair costs depend on the specific issue — HDMI port damage involving motherboard trace repair is more expensive than a basic port swap, while overheating cleaning and thermal paste replacement is one of the most cost-effective repairs available for the value it delivers in extending your console's lifespan. <a href="https://www.playstation.com/en-ca/support/hardware/ps5/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ps5-context-link">Sony's PS5 support centre</a> provides troubleshooting guides that can help determine whether a repair is needed before visiting.</p>
        <p class="ps5-context-paragraph">Many customers are surprised that a PS5 HDMI repair can approach a significant fraction of the console's current value, particularly when motherboard trace damage is involved. <a href="https://www.ifixit.com/Search?query=ps5+teardown" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ps5-context-link">iFixit's PS5 teardown</a> reveals exactly why — the HDMI port is soldered directly to the main motherboard with no daughter board, making pad and trace repair an essential skill for anyone servicing these consoles.</p>
        <p class="ps5-context-paragraph">If the repair cost doesn't make financial sense given your console's condition, we'll explain that clearly and walk you through alternatives — including trade-in options toward a newer console or a refurbished PS5 from our pre-owned inventory.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
